OL,3,CMajor search underway for boy, 15,
OL,4,Cmissing in water at nature reserve
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,FHampshire Police said: "A multi-agency
OL,8,Foperation is underway following a
OL,9,Freport that a 15-year-old boy is
OL,10,Fmissing after he was last seen
OL,11,Fswimming at Testwood Lakes near
OL,12,FBlackwater.
OL,14,F"This was reported to police at 1:35pm
OL,15,Fon Wednesday 24 June and the area is
OL,16,Fcurrently off limits while our search
OL,17,Foperation is ongoing. Please avoid the
OL,18,Farea at this time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
