OL,3,CMajor search underway for boy, 15,
OL,4,Cmissing in water at nature reserve
OL,6,F"We have deployed the marine units to
OL,7,Faid in the search, alongside
OL,8,Fcolleagues from NPAS, South Central
OL,9,FAmbulance Service, and Hampshire &
OL,10,FIsle of Wight Fire Service."
OL,12,FThe main gate to the lakes has been
OL,13,Fclosed and people are urged to avoid
OL,14,Fthe area.
OL,16,FMore follows.
